headline: Seagate Recasts Role As AI Storage Partner With Undervalued Shares
summary: Seagate Technology Holdings (NasdaqGS:STX) has shifted its focus toward AI driven storage demand, supported by partnerships with large hyperscale cloud providers. The company reports that these partnerships are now backing its core technology roadmap and that future capacity bookings for AI infrastructure are strong.
